---
import '../styles/global.css';
const lastUpdated = '16 April 2026';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Refund Policy — Aethelgard</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Aethelgard's refund policy. 14-day no-questions-asked refund." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-neutral-900 font-sans antialiased">

  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-navy-900 border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-white font-black tracking-tight text-lg">Aethelgard</a>
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">← Home</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="bg-navy-900 py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-10 text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-neutral-900 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded-2xl p-6">
          We offer a <strong>14-day, no-questions-asked refund</strong> on all Aethelgard licenses — Annual and Lifetime. If the product doesn't work for you, email us and we'll process a full refund immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">How to request a refund</h2>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:contact@aethelgard.finance" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium">contact@aethelgard.finance</a> within 14 days of your purchase with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>The email address used at checkout</li>
          <li>Your order reference (in your Paddle receipt)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We will process the refund within 2 business days. Paddle typically returns funds to your original payment method within 5–10 business days depending on your bank.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">After a refund</h2>
        <p>Upon refund, your license key is deactivated. The Software continues to function in Personal-tier (free) mode — you do not lose access to your data. Your financial records remain on your device and are yours to keep.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">Annual renewals</h2>
        <p>Annual licenses do not auto-renew. When your license expires, the Software returns to Personal-tier functionality. You will not be charged automatically. If you choose to renew, you purchase a new license at the then-current price.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">Upgrading from Annual to Lifetime</h2>
        <p>If you hold a current Annual license and wish to upgrade to Lifetime, follow these steps — <strong>do not purchase the Lifetime plan directly</strong>, as we will not be able to apply your credit retroactively.</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Email <a href="mailto:contact@aethelgard.finance" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium">contact@aethelgard.finance</a> with the subject <strong>"Upgrade to Lifetime"</strong>, including the email address used at checkout.</li>
          <li>We will calculate the unused portion of your Annual license and reply with a personalised discount code covering that amount.</li>
          <li>Once you have received the discount code, purchase the Lifetime plan for your tier from the <a href="/#pricing" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium">pricing page</a> and apply the code at checkout.</li>
          <li>Your new Lifetime license key will be delivered automatically to your email.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">We aim to respond to upgrade requests within one business day.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">Questions</h2>
        <p>Any questions about billing or refunds: <a href="mailto:contact@aethelgard.finance" class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 font-medium">contact@aethelgard.finance</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-navy-900 py-8 px-6 mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-white/30 text-xs">
      <div class="space-y-1 text-center sm:text-left">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Aethelgard. All rights reserved.</span>
        <p class="text-white/20">2B Connected Ltd · Registered in England &amp; Wales · Company No. 06427186</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">Terms</a>
        <a href="/refunds" class="text-white/60">Refunds</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
